snippet.title: String Avoider
snippet.description: String Avoider Avoid the walls and guide your string through all 26 levels. Hit the scissor to cut the string in half.

snippet.title: Hashi
snippet.description: Hashi Puzzle game. Try to connect all islands using the amount of bridges displayed on each island.

snippet.title: Swindler 2
snippet.description: Swindler 2 Action game. Collect the stars and reach the exit using your goo string to steer through the levels.

snippet.title: Mecha Arena
snippet.description: Mecha Arena RPG game. Make the mecha you own the stringest one around and win all battles with it.
